WEBVTT

00:06.500 --> 00:09.416
NETFLIX PRESENTS

00:22.541 --> 00:24.083
My name is Maca.

00:24.166 --> 00:25.958
I'm 29 years old.

00:26.041 --> 00:29.458
I've spent 28 of those years as a loser,
but I'm evolving.

00:29.541 --> 00:30.750
I'm becoming…

00:33.291 --> 00:34.958
a cool girl.

00:54.041 --> 00:56.125
-I can't do it!
-Come on, Adri.

00:56.208 --> 01:00.208
-Are you shitting me? We're all doing it.
-What? It looks great like this.

01:01.541 --> 01:03.166
Looks like a pair of DDs.

01:04.041 --> 01:05.916
More like As.

01:06.416 --> 01:09.041
Honestly, I've never been a fan of pain.

01:09.125 --> 01:13.083
No pain like the pain of feeling weak.
You're not weak.

01:19.833 --> 01:20.666
Let's do this.

01:23.958 --> 01:28.291
Okay… I believe in love
more than anything.

01:29.083 --> 01:31.875
I believe in Julián, the family book,

01:31.958 --> 01:34.708
Sunday lunches with my mother-in-law,

01:34.791 --> 01:39.083
wedding anniversaries,
and I really believe in our mortgage.

01:43.541 --> 01:45.416
Now's not the time to get into it.

01:45.500 --> 01:48.666
Adriana already knows
what I think of her marriage.

01:50.958 --> 01:53.041
-Yeah, you like that?
-I love it.

01:53.541 --> 01:54.666
Come here, babe.

01:54.750 --> 01:56.791
No, don't worry about me. Cum.

01:58.166 --> 02:01.541
She's trying to convince us
that she could be asexual.

02:02.666 --> 02:06.541
Just because you said "I do"
doesn't mean you have to settle for less.

02:10.625 --> 02:13.875
I've told her
there's no way she's asexual.

02:13.958 --> 02:16.708
Is it true that
in some tribes in Papua New Guinea,

02:16.791 --> 02:19.166
tattoos are used to summon the dead?

02:19.250 --> 02:22.833
Jimena and Santi were dating the day
he crossed the street without looking.

02:22.916 --> 02:24.750
That was 11 years ago.

02:25.250 --> 02:27.791
I gotta choose
between the triple-camera one

02:27.875 --> 02:30.375
and the one with insane memory.

02:31.000 --> 02:32.250
What do you think?

02:32.333 --> 02:36.166
Since then, she's been obsessed
with Nesquik and seeing him again.

02:36.250 --> 02:40.166
Her latest attempt came from Indonesia.
Reincarnation salts.

02:40.666 --> 02:44.666
Santi's spirit is on the way
for 200 dollars plus shipping.

02:45.541 --> 02:49.416
Jime's convinced Santi will be back
in the flesh sooner or later,

02:49.500 --> 02:52.291
so she looks for him where the flesh is.

02:54.000 --> 02:56.958
But they always do or say something
Santi never would've.

02:57.041 --> 02:59.750
And then, of course,
the search begins again.

03:02.250 --> 03:04.000
I'm not perfect either.

03:04.083 --> 03:07.916
I wish I were more confident,
stronger, didn't care what people think.

03:08.708 --> 03:09.833
But I'm working on it.

03:12.375 --> 03:13.708
It was declined.

03:15.833 --> 03:17.958
-Shoot.
-Typical.

03:18.875 --> 03:21.125
Think of it as me
helping you become empowered.

03:25.250 --> 03:27.458
But he's cute. That's all I need.

03:29.625 --> 03:31.208
I see him once a week.

03:31.708 --> 03:36.208
We don't do movies
or shopping or dinners, none of that shit.

03:36.708 --> 03:39.666
It leaves me free to do my own thing.

03:39.750 --> 03:43.666
Being coupled up is like
being swallowed by a mental black hole.

03:43.750 --> 03:45.333
It's a distraction.

03:46.083 --> 03:49.083
I go out on my own,
and I have sex with him.

03:52.333 --> 03:55.958
Don't get me wrong.
I used to be a hopeless romantic, but then

03:57.041 --> 03:58.000
I saw the light.

04:07.958 --> 04:09.625
-Turn that off.
-What?

04:10.416 --> 04:11.791
Turn that off, dammit!

04:12.500 --> 04:14.291
Quick! Turn that off before--

04:47.333 --> 04:48.791
What the hell was that?

04:51.083 --> 04:52.875
I said I was working on it, okay?

04:56.208 --> 04:58.750
But it sucks
to always be talking about men.

04:59.375 --> 05:00.750
Let's talk about me.

05:01.250 --> 05:04.458
Watch it! The matcha
can't mix with the soy milk. Shit.

05:05.541 --> 05:06.583
Good morning.

05:06.666 --> 05:10.916
I've posted the photo I edited yesterday
with the hashtag #AdoptDontShop.

05:11.000 --> 05:13.958
And I got Andrés Sardá
to do your gown for the ceremony

05:14.041 --> 05:15.708
and ODYSSEY to do your makeup.

05:15.791 --> 05:18.125
And I'm finishing up your speech now.

05:18.208 --> 05:20.958
-As soon as it's done--
-Maca, what's this?

05:22.583 --> 05:26.125
-Your matcha.
-I told you about it in a voice message.

05:27.041 --> 05:29.958
-A voice message?
-Yes, sweetie, a voice message.

05:31.416 --> 05:33.000
At four in the morning.

05:33.083 --> 05:36.250
I'm trying a new diet.
No eating for 20 hours a day.

05:37.000 --> 05:41.250
What? Women in Kolkata have been doing it
for centuries. They look great.

05:42.166 --> 05:45.250
Are you sure they're choosing to fast?

05:45.333 --> 05:46.208
What?

05:47.500 --> 05:51.458
-Never mind. I'll have it.
-I don't want any temptations nearby.

05:51.541 --> 05:54.875
Okay? So, when you're with me,
you have to pretend you're fasting too.

05:54.958 --> 05:56.041
For solidarity.

05:57.125 --> 05:59.875
And Maca, I want you in heels.
You know that.

05:59.958 --> 06:02.083
Sometimes I just can't with you.

06:06.541 --> 06:09.125
I don't wear heels
because I refuse to get blisters

06:09.208 --> 06:12.916
for someone who pays me under the table,
makes me work weekends,

06:13.000 --> 06:15.208
and is now having me starve to death.

06:15.708 --> 06:17.333
How about a bit of respect?

06:22.500 --> 06:26.791
Let's talk about the ulcer I'm getting
from not daring to speak my mind to Pipa,

06:26.875 --> 06:29.000
my unbearable and tyrannical boss.

06:29.708 --> 06:34.250
But slaves don't complain,
and that's basically what I am to her.

06:34.833 --> 06:37.875
I started working for Pipa
a year and a half ago,

06:37.958 --> 06:40.416
when I didn't believe in myself at all.

06:40.500 --> 06:42.250
To be fair, she never lied to me.

06:42.958 --> 06:45.833
You'll do it all,
but you won't get any credit.

06:45.916 --> 06:48.791
Photos, writing, tying my shoelaces.

06:48.875 --> 06:52.125
I'll pay you very little.
I'll demand a lot.

06:52.208 --> 06:53.625
And I'll make you cry.

06:54.291 --> 06:57.916
But it won't be my fault.
I was diagnosed as a psychopath.

06:58.000 --> 07:02.583
So, I guess I couldn't care less
about your feelings.

07:06.666 --> 07:07.833
When can I start?

07:14.583 --> 07:18.125
Pipa is ninth
in the national ranking of influencers.

07:18.625 --> 07:21.125
She's gone up 12 positions
since last year.

07:21.208 --> 07:23.500
-Pipa!
-Pipa!

07:23.583 --> 07:25.916
She thinks it's the new vintage filter.

07:26.791 --> 07:29.416
But I think there's another reason for it.

07:29.500 --> 07:31.375
Pipa! Over here.

07:47.083 --> 07:51.708
And Best Communication
on Social Media goes to

07:52.791 --> 07:53.958
Pipa!

07:57.250 --> 07:58.416
Thank you.

08:07.958 --> 08:09.375
Thank you very much.

08:09.916 --> 08:11.958
I'm… a little nervous.

08:14.208 --> 08:17.875
Just one post
can reach thousands of people.

08:18.458 --> 08:23.125
We have the responsibility
and duty to change things.

08:23.208 --> 08:25.083
It's the art of communicating.

08:25.750 --> 08:29.125
Thank you to my followers
and all of you here today.

08:29.208 --> 08:31.250
Thank you from the bottom of my heart.

08:35.291 --> 08:41.000
I never could have won this award
without the help of…

08:44.416 --> 08:47.791
My Boost-Up Serum Magic Fresh Light
by Ophalo.

08:47.875 --> 08:51.208
Available for 25 euros
in department stores. Thank you!

09:05.125 --> 09:06.250
Oh, shit.

09:16.625 --> 09:20.458
Hello? Is someone there?
Anyone have a tampon?

09:21.250 --> 09:23.458
Yeah. I've got something even better.

09:25.000 --> 09:27.625
I keep one of these on me to give away.

09:28.291 --> 09:30.666
Just try it. You'll love it. You'll see.

09:33.000 --> 09:38.500
I've been trying to use a cup for months,
but I can never get the hang of it.

09:39.000 --> 09:41.958
This is my brand, and they're easy to use.

09:42.041 --> 09:43.625
-Raquel?
-Yeah?

09:43.708 --> 09:45.375
Raquel, it's me, Maca.

09:45.458 --> 09:47.750
Maca, honey.

09:47.833 --> 09:50.333
Of course. I saw Pipa,
and I thought of you.

09:50.416 --> 09:51.750
About the cup, listen.

09:51.833 --> 09:54.750
Grab the wide part with your fingers.

09:55.125 --> 09:57.625
And it'll go in a lot easier. You'll see.

09:58.541 --> 09:59.375
All right.

09:59.458 --> 10:01.708
-Got it?
-Just a second. Let me try.

10:04.250 --> 10:05.208
Okay.

10:07.208 --> 10:10.458
Yeah. It went in perfectly.

10:10.958 --> 10:14.125
-They're something else, right?
-They're wonderful.

10:15.750 --> 10:17.375
-Raquel.
-Maca.

10:19.000 --> 10:21.666
-You look great.
-Congrats on your awards.

10:21.750 --> 10:24.291
Thanks. It's always nice
to get recognition.

10:24.375 --> 10:27.583
-How are you?
-Swamped, as always.

10:28.375 --> 10:29.875
Pipa is such a diva.

10:30.375 --> 10:35.541
I keep telling you, with your potential,
agencies should be fighting over you.

10:35.625 --> 10:37.875
Yeah. I just don't know
if that's what I want.

10:37.958 --> 10:40.458
Well, you certainly don't want
to be exploited.

10:40.541 --> 10:41.708
No, definitely not.

10:42.208 --> 10:44.625
It's time you made new contacts.

10:47.541 --> 10:49.875
-Stand up for yourself.
-For me? Really?

10:49.958 --> 10:51.291
You deserve it.

10:54.875 --> 10:55.833
Thanks.

10:56.958 --> 10:59.708
Well, I'm off.
This is a snoozefest, and I have a date.

10:59.791 --> 11:01.583
-Have fun!
-Thanks.

11:01.666 --> 11:03.083
-Bye.
-Bye.

11:51.083 --> 11:52.166
Pipa!

11:52.250 --> 11:55.750
I put in tons of overtime
yesterday and the day before, so…

11:55.833 --> 11:56.666
So?

11:57.166 --> 12:00.416
So… I'm going home.
You'll have to get back on your own.

12:01.500 --> 12:03.916
And tomorrow, I'm coming in at 11:00.
No, 12:00.

12:05.291 --> 12:06.333
Oh, sweetie.

12:07.291 --> 12:08.916
-What?
-Look at your feet.

12:09.000 --> 12:10.583
You think that's okay?

12:10.666 --> 12:12.166
I ask you to dress well,

12:12.250 --> 12:15.000
and you pick today of all days
to publicly embarrass me.

12:15.708 --> 12:17.625
Well, Converse are in again.

12:17.708 --> 12:21.083
Yeah. If you're cool enough
to pull them off.

12:23.291 --> 12:25.500
Poor thing. She's clueless.

12:48.916 --> 12:51.250
Okay. They're expensive.
And I need the job.

12:51.333 --> 12:54.458
Plus, I can't afford to make a huge scene.

12:56.625 --> 12:59.500
Girls, you won't believe
what Pipa just did.

12:59.583 --> 13:01.625
She's the fucking worst.

13:01.708 --> 13:03.791
I was in the bathroom,
and I ran into Raquel,

13:03.875 --> 13:06.833
that influencer I told you about,
who's super nice.

13:07.416 --> 13:08.666
Raquel.

14:27.583 --> 14:28.708
Shit.

14:29.208 --> 14:30.541
Leo's back.

14:33.500 --> 14:35.041
And he's with Raquel.

14:56.791 --> 14:58.500
-What's your name?
-Macarena.

14:58.583 --> 15:00.541
Do you go by Maca or Macarena?

15:00.625 --> 15:01.583
Maca.

15:01.666 --> 15:04.666
Maca. I love that name, "Maca."
Here's to you, Maca.

15:06.416 --> 15:08.625
-And what's your name?
-I'm Leo.

15:11.916 --> 15:13.166
No toast for me, then?

15:19.625 --> 15:23.000
It was the deepest,
most passionate experience of my life.

15:24.541 --> 15:26.250
Since that first look.

15:38.583 --> 15:43.500
All the joy movies had promised me
seemed real and infinite.

15:48.625 --> 15:49.958
Okay, recite…

15:50.708 --> 15:52.750
Section 66, point two?

15:52.833 --> 15:56.833
"When there are
two or more mitigating circumstances,

15:56.916 --> 16:01.083
the court shall impose… the punishment
that is lesser by one or two degrees

16:01.166 --> 16:02.916
to that established by law."

16:17.833 --> 16:20.291
Maca, you know
I can't stand it when you do that.

16:20.375 --> 16:23.125
-I'm the one who can't stand you.
-No, I can't stand you.

16:23.541 --> 16:25.375
-You're such an idiot.
-Shut up.

16:27.791 --> 16:29.750
Our connection was intense.

16:30.333 --> 16:31.958
So intense.

16:33.666 --> 16:37.583
I felt like what we had was unique

16:37.666 --> 16:39.750
and could never be repeated
with anyone else.

16:40.375 --> 16:41.416
Ever.

16:47.083 --> 16:48.916
But one day, he disappeared.

16:49.416 --> 16:53.125
He up and left the life
we'd planned together.

16:57.166 --> 16:59.000
He never apologized.

17:00.458 --> 17:01.500
He just left.

17:02.000 --> 17:06.208
And I ended up stuck,
believing I'd never be happy without him.

17:14.125 --> 17:15.875
What are you guys doing here?

17:17.416 --> 17:20.166
-Come on.
-But… Close the door.

17:20.750 --> 17:24.833
-Let me guess, you haven't slept at all?
-All right. Who needs coffee?

17:24.916 --> 17:27.250
-No.
-No.

17:27.333 --> 17:28.833
-Maca, get up.
-Get up.

17:28.916 --> 17:31.333
-Help me, Adri.
-I'm fine. For real, okay?

17:32.500 --> 17:34.166
-But--
-Come on.

17:34.250 --> 17:36.500
-Now pants.
-All right. Come on.

17:36.583 --> 17:39.291
-Can't we just sleep for a teeny bit more?
-No.

17:39.375 --> 17:41.583
All right. Let's have breakfast.

17:44.833 --> 17:45.833
Excuse me.

17:48.375 --> 17:51.666
Carbs are good. Carbs are great.

17:52.500 --> 17:55.125
I put a hex on him
so he'd go back to Boston.

17:55.208 --> 17:57.958
-And get crabs. The cherry on top.
-I'm fine.

17:58.041 --> 18:00.333
Girls, I am fine.

18:04.750 --> 18:08.416
You sent this at four in the morning.
Wait till you hear what you sent at five.

18:08.500 --> 18:09.500
Well, okay.

18:10.625 --> 18:12.750
It wasn't my best night.

18:13.916 --> 18:14.875
Leo…

18:16.791 --> 18:21.375
Leo was an important person in my life,
and he left me with some… issues.

18:21.916 --> 18:23.291
Thanks.

18:25.791 --> 18:26.666
"Issues"?

18:27.791 --> 18:30.833
Okay, fine.
He gave me… fucking romantic PTSD.

18:31.333 --> 18:34.375
But now I see things differently.
I understand it.

18:34.458 --> 18:36.666
I know it's our immature society's fault

18:36.750 --> 18:39.250
for making us, especially women,
believe in fairy tales.

18:42.333 --> 18:44.166
You're handling it better this time.

18:45.750 --> 18:48.083
Someone who hurt me
and didn't even apologize

18:48.166 --> 18:49.958
doesn't deserve my attention.

18:50.041 --> 18:54.291
I'm still on my way to feeling confident.
This doesn't change a thing. Not a thing.

18:55.791 --> 18:56.625
How'd he look?

18:58.333 --> 19:00.375
Still got that hunter-gatherer ass?

19:00.458 --> 19:03.583
You help by comforting her.
I help by saying shit's gonna hit the fan.

19:03.666 --> 19:06.208
Jime, I'm the new Maca.

19:06.291 --> 19:08.458
I'm Maca 2.0.

19:09.041 --> 19:10.375
Trust me.

19:12.083 --> 19:13.875
You know you need to shower, right?

19:13.958 --> 19:15.083
-Yeah. I will.
-Yeah.

19:16.208 --> 19:17.166
All right.

19:17.708 --> 19:18.916
Bye, girls.

19:20.041 --> 19:21.541
-Take care of yourself.
-Shower.

19:21.625 --> 19:23.500
-Thanks.
-You're such a bitch.

19:24.208 --> 19:25.583
-Bye, Maca.
-Bye.

19:28.125 --> 19:30.000
Did you buy what she said about Leo?

19:31.000 --> 19:33.625
She had 12 churros
and hot chocolate. She's fine.

19:33.708 --> 19:35.625
Are you for real? "Maca 2.0"?

19:35.708 --> 19:37.166
-Adri, come on.
-Jime.

19:37.250 --> 19:40.208
-She's not even Maca 1.5.
-People can change.

19:40.291 --> 19:41.208
-Oh yeah?
-Yeah.

19:41.291 --> 19:44.375
Well, maybe you'll surprise us
and turn into a sex maniac.

19:45.708 --> 19:46.541
Oh!

19:52.041 --> 19:52.875
How about you?

19:52.958 --> 19:55.666
-Thought about seeing a psychologist?
-What?

19:56.958 --> 19:57.833
Jime.

19:59.125 --> 20:03.208
You're unbelievable.
Jime! Where are you going?

20:04.416 --> 20:06.041
I can't believe this.

20:37.958 --> 20:39.041
Excuse me.

20:39.125 --> 20:40.458
It's an emergency.

20:41.416 --> 20:42.750
My back.

20:44.500 --> 20:46.708
-It's killing me.
-Do you have an appointment?

20:47.208 --> 20:51.166
No. It just happened today.
I woke up like this.

20:51.250 --> 20:53.375
I need to be seen
by the guy who just came in.

20:53.458 --> 20:54.750
-Samuel?
-Yes.

20:54.833 --> 20:56.166
Yeah, Samuel.

20:56.250 --> 20:58.083
I mean, Samu.

20:58.166 --> 21:00.708
Are you a patient of his,
a relative, a friend?

21:01.208 --> 21:03.541
No. Not yet.

21:03.625 --> 21:06.791
You'll have to make an appointment.
We don't handle emergencies.

21:06.875 --> 21:09.166
Please, it's important.

21:09.250 --> 21:13.000
-We're all booked--
-Samuel! I need you to check out… my back.

21:13.500 --> 21:14.625
It's killing me.

21:14.708 --> 21:18.583
-I can barely walk or do anything.
-Do you have an appointment?

21:18.666 --> 21:21.166
-No. She just showed up.
-Get her info.

21:21.250 --> 21:24.500
We'll give you
the first opening we have this week. Okay?

21:27.541 --> 21:29.291
Hey, calm down.

21:29.375 --> 21:31.083
I can take a quick look.

21:31.166 --> 21:32.416
-Head on in.
-Okay.

21:34.291 --> 21:37.541
-If José Luis comes, ask him to wait.
-All right.

21:41.125 --> 21:44.125
Tell me what's going on.
I didn't quite get it.

21:44.208 --> 21:47.541
Okay. Well, look, my entire back hurts.

21:48.041 --> 21:49.041
All of it.

21:49.541 --> 21:51.625
From top to bottom.

21:52.583 --> 21:53.500
Even here.

21:54.708 --> 21:58.791
This is where it hurts the most.
I can barely sit in a chair.

21:58.875 --> 22:00.416
-All right.
-Here, my butt.

22:00.500 --> 22:01.750
The sacrum, then?

22:01.833 --> 22:04.875
-Sacrum, butt, whatever.
-Let's take a look.

22:04.958 --> 22:05.791
Okay.

22:15.166 --> 22:17.208
-Can I ask you something?
-Yeah?

22:17.291 --> 22:22.250
Does the name… Santi Asenjo… ring a bell?

22:22.333 --> 22:23.875
-Who?
-Oh, right.

22:23.958 --> 22:27.041
When someone is reincarnated,
they don't know it.

22:27.125 --> 22:30.750
I don't know what you're talking about.
Let's see. Hold on.

22:30.833 --> 22:32.791
If I press here, does it hurt?

22:32.875 --> 22:36.166
-You're not groaning as much as before.
-Let's see.

22:38.041 --> 22:40.166
-Does that hurt?
-It hurts a lot.

22:40.250 --> 22:42.250
-All right.
-Yeah, it really does.

22:44.625 --> 22:48.250
Even if you don't remember him,
I bet you like the same stuff.

22:48.333 --> 22:52.041
You must remember Aragorn's sword
in the battle of Morannon.

22:52.125 --> 22:54.750
"I bid you stand, Men of the East!"

22:55.250 --> 22:57.750
-Take a deep breath in for me, okay?
-Sure.

22:59.875 --> 23:00.958
Let it out.

23:06.541 --> 23:07.708
Holy shit!

23:10.291 --> 23:14.375
That's all the time I have.
Have Marta schedule you for this week.

23:14.458 --> 23:16.041
-Your back's a mess.
-Sure.

23:16.125 --> 23:17.166
-Okay?
-Okay.

23:19.250 --> 23:23.291
And it's, "I bid you stand,
Men of the West." Okay?

23:27.208 --> 23:28.041
Hell yes!

23:41.791 --> 23:43.375
Hello. Can I help you?

23:44.375 --> 23:45.708
Can I help you?

23:45.791 --> 23:47.291
No, can I help you?

