Always saying one thing and doing another.

34:07.416 --> 34:08.958
What do you mean?

34:10.208 --> 34:13.458
To be clear,
I want to screw him over

34:13.541 --> 34:16.958
because it's not fair that things
are going so well for him.

34:17.041 --> 34:18.875
But I also want to rescue her.

34:18.958 --> 34:22.166
Wouldn't you warn someone
before they fell into a well?

34:22.666 --> 34:27.291
I wish someone had given me
that spoiler back then. Sisterhood.

34:28.541 --> 34:33.166
Well, he threw my heart onto the floor
and then danced on it

34:33.250 --> 34:35.916
until it was nothing but trampled mush.

34:38.208 --> 34:41.791
-But what happened?
-He's the biggest asshole I've ever met.

34:41.875 --> 34:45.375
He threw me away like I was nothing.
He destroyed my future.

34:45.458 --> 34:50.208
I'll just give you one piece of advice.
Run. Run away and never look back.

34:50.708 --> 34:52.958
Oops, I gotta go. It's getting late.

34:55.583 --> 34:56.583
Everything okay?

34:59.916 --> 35:03.500
-How are you doing this week, Jimena?
-Great, actually.

35:04.333 --> 35:08.708
