37:18.666 --> 37:19.541
Well…

37:22.666 --> 37:23.833
A toast?

37:25.000 --> 37:26.958
-To tonight.
-To tonight.

37:27.458 --> 37:29.166
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

37:50.416 --> 37:51.250
Come here.

38:46.291 --> 38:47.125
Come here.

39:31.750 --> 39:34.000
-Macarena Bartual?
