40:38.958 --> 40:41.041
The insanity of love.

40:41.125 --> 40:44.125
You mean,
falling for someone big time, right?

40:44.208 --> 40:48.458
Falling for someone, not being able
to tell expectations from reality.

40:49.041 --> 40:53.333
Authors from this period describe
a woman's experience of love as…

40:53.416 --> 40:54.333
agonizing.

40:54.416 --> 40:57.458
