almost like a mental illness.

40:57.958 --> 40:59.125
And perhaps it was.

40:59.208 --> 41:03.416
Honestly, I expected more sensitivity
from a literature professor.

41:06.416 --> 41:07.250
What are you…?

41:08.916 --> 41:09.750
