my emotional competence.

41:19.041 --> 41:22.500
Of course not.
You can't debate what doesn't exist.

41:22.583 --> 41:24.208
All right. Just a minute.

41:24.291 --> 41:29.583
I'm talking about a specific period
in 19th-century literature.

41:29.666 --> 41:33.708
